---

## Mocking Principles

| Mock | Don't Mock |
|------|------------|
| External APIs | Code under test |
| Database (unit) | Simple deps |
| Network | Pure functions |

---

## Review Checklist

- [ ] Coverage 80%+ on critical paths
- [ ] AAA pattern followed
- [ ] Tests are isolated
- [ ] Descriptive naming
- [ ] Edge cases covered
- [ ] External deps mocked
