## Anti-Patterns

| ❌ Don't | ✅ Do |
|----------|-------|
| Test implementation | Test behavior |
| Multiple asserts | One per test |
| Dependent tests | Independent |
| Ignore flaky | Fix root cause |
| Skip cleanup | Always reset |

